001package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.processor.conditions;
002
003import java.lang.annotation.ElementType;
004import java.lang.annotation.Retention;
005import java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;
006import java.lang.annotation.Target;
007
008/**
009 * Expect that a field is always less than a value. The type of the field will be used to pick which value is read
010 *
011 * @since 2.0.0
012 */
013@Target({ ElementType.FIELD })
014@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
015public @interface ExpectLessThan {
016    /**
017     * The value as an integer
018     *
019     * @return The value as an integer
020     *
021     * @since 2.0.0
022     */
023    int intValue() default Integer.MAX_VALUE;
024
025    /**
026     * The value as a long
027     *
028     * @return The value as a long
029     *
030     * @since 2.0.0
031     */
032    long longValue() default Long.MAX_VALUE;
033
034    /**
035     * The value as a float
036     *
037     * @return The value as a float
038     *
039     * @since 2.0.0
040     */
041    float floatValue() default Float.MAX_VALUE;
042
043    /**
044     * The value as a double
045     *
046     * @return The value as a double
047     *
048     * @since 2.0.0
049     */
050    double doubleValue() default Double.MAX_VALUE;
051
052    /**
053     * If the check should be less than or equal to instead of less than
054     *
055     * @return If the check should be less than or equal to instead of less than
056     *
057     * @since 2.0.0
058     */
059    boolean orEqual() default false;
060}
